

    Achievements System
        "First Million" for reaching 1M minerals
        "Click Master" for 1000 clicks
        "Upgrade Collector" for buying all upgrades
        Cool badges and rewards for each achievement

    Prestige System
        Reset progress for permanent multipliers
        Special prestige-only upgrades
        New game mechanics unlock after prestige

    Random Events
        Golden asteroids that give bonus minerals
        Meteor showers multiplying earnings
        Time-limited bonus periods

    Sound Effects
        Satisfying click sounds
        Upgrade purchase chimes
        Achievement jingles

    Different Game Zones
        Moon mining
        Mars expedition
        Deep space exploration
        Each with unique bonuses
